Keyforge Deck Name Analysis

Words in Keyforge decks are exclusive to certain houses.

Based on a Reddit thread that pointed me to a particularity of the Keyforge deck name generation algorithm, I have done an analysis of a dump of every deck provided by Decks Of Keyforge and found all the words excluvie to a certain Keyforge house!

Below are charts that show the top 30 exclusive words for a house, and how many deck names have that words in them.

All words below are 100% exclusive to their house.

I have uploaded the full dataset to explore at this google drive folder and you can find slightly prettier versions of these graphs here.

Theres further analysis to be done here. I noticed that certain words are nearly exclusive to a house, but not entirely. I should be able to get a p-value for a confidence threshold for exclusiveness; but I got a lil stuck on the probability math.

As well, I applied this same analysis to see if certain words are exclusive to certain cards, but came up empty.

Im not sure why certain houses seem to have a much higher number of certain words than other houses. Brobnar has 800 Club decks, but the highest Untamed word is Banjo at 42. Some exploratory analysis might reveal something interesting.

Once I get around to it, I plan on adding on adding some interactivity to these charts, as well as adding a Deck Name Analyzer to show if your deck contains any exclusive words in it.

If anyone finds anything interesting to share, or finds anything wrong with my reports, feel free to reach out to me on Reddit or Twitter.
